      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, characterized by its meticulous maintenance record and exemplary mechanical performance. This unit represents a superior balance of sophistication and reliability, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards. The interior remains remarkably preserved, complemented by a robust powertrain that delivers a refined driving experience. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a well-curated automobile that is fully prepared for immediate service.",
